    "Two different grids over a torus defined using different subsets of A 1, A 2, A 3, B 1, B 2, B 3.",
    "Edge labels indicate adjacency matrices that generate the respective edges.",
    "By extracting either horizontal or vertical strips from these grids, we obtain planar 'wheel graphs' whose union contains all edges in the Tanner graph.",
